OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMining giant pleads guilty 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto UK bribery charges      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A subsidiary of the mining and         
OL,6, commodities trading giant Glencore has 
OL,7, pleaded guilty to seven counts of      
OL,8, bribery in a London court.             
OL,10,FThe firm also said it will pay more    
OL,11,Fthan $1bn (#800m) to resolve similar   
OL,12,Fclaims with the US and Brazil.         
OL,14,FThe UK's Serious Fraud Office said it  
OL,15,Fhad exposed "profit-driven bribery and 
OL,16,Fcorruption" across Glencore Energy UK's
OL,17,Foil operations in five African nations.
OL,19,FThe firm will find how much it must pay
OL,20,Fin fines at a sentencing in June.      
